quran[8{c,v,t}:
30,25,"aur uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke aasman aur zameen is ke hukum se qaim hain phir jounhi ke uss ne tumhe zameen se puraka, bas aik hi pukaar mein achanak tum nikal aao ge"
30,26,"asmano aur zameen mein jo bhi hain uss ke bande hain, sab ke sab isi ke tabay farmaan hain"
30,27,"wohi hai jo takhleeq ki ibtida karta hai, phir wohi is ka iada kere ga aur yeh is ke liye aasaan tar hai asmano aur zameen mein is ki sift sab se bartar hai aur woh zabardast aur hakeem hai"
30,28,woh tumhe khud tumhari apni hi zaat se aik misaal deta hai kya tumahray unn ghulamoo mein se jo tumhari malkiat mein hain kuch ghulam aisay bhi hain jo hamaray diye hue maal o doulat mein tumahray sath barabar ke shareek hon aur tum unn se uss terhan drtay ho jis terhan aapas mein apne peghambron se drtay ho? is terhan hum ayaat khol kar paish karte hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain
30,29,magar yeh zalim be samjhay boojhay apne takhayulaat ke peechay chal parre hain ab kon uss shakhs ko rasta dikha sakta hai jisay Allah ne bhatka diya ho aisay logon ka to koi madad gaar nahi ho sakta
30,30,"pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aur NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke پیروؤں ) yak soo ho kar apna rukh iss deen ki simt mein jama do, qaim ho jao uss fitrat par jis par Allah taala ne insanon ko peda kya hai, Allah ki banai hui saakht badli nahi ja sakti, yahi bilkul raast aur durust deen hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
30,31,"( qaim ho jao iss baat par ) Allah ki taraf rujoo karte hue, aur daro uss se, aur namaz qaim karo, aur nah ho jao unn mushriqeen mein se"
30,32,"jinhon ne apna apna deen allag bana liya hai aur garohoon mein Butt gay hain, har aik giroh ke paas jo kuch hai isi mein woh magan hai"
